{"word":"προσωτέρω","slug":"προσωτέρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσωτέρω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> and <a href='S:Superlative'>superl.</a> of <a href='S:πρόσω'><el>πρόσω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>further on, further</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>further than</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>πορρ. τοῦ καιροῦ</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—also with the <a href='S:Article'>Art.</a>, <el>τὸ προσωτέρω</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>further from</i>, <el>τῶν πυλῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>προσωτάτω</el>, attic <el>πορρωτάτω</el> <i>furthest</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>τὰ προσωτάτω</el> <i>the furthest parts</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; also <el>προσώτατα</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:— <el>ὡς προσωτάτω</el> <i>as far as possible</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>furthest from</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}